45:00.281 --> 45:03.068
You expect me to believe
she'd allow you to move to a town...

45:03.242 --> 45:05.324
...in the middle of a swamp
and date a waitress?

45:05.494 --> 45:07.075
[RUSSELL CHUCKLES]

45:11.709 --> 45:14.576
I know you're still working for her...

45:15.630 --> 45:18.337
...and I know she has secrets...

45:18.507 --> 45:21.294
...and I wanna know what they are.

45:21.469 --> 45:24.961
In return, I'll make you sheriff of Area 2.

45:25.139 --> 45:29.303
Perhaps Your Majesty is using werewolves
to gather his intelligence as well.

45:29.602 --> 45:30.682
Ouch.

45:30.853 --> 45:31.888
[CHUCKLES]

45:32.063 --> 45:34.224
BILL:
There's clearly been a mistake.

45:35.107 --> 45:37.974
I am not the vampire you are looking for.

45:38.152 --> 45:41.235
I am not privy to the queen's secrets...

45:41.656 --> 45:46.070
...nor do I have any interest
in being your sheriff.

45:46.953 --> 45:50.946
-I'm sorry to waste your time.
RUSSELL: Poor Sookie.

45:51.123 --> 45:54.991
Such a shame she has to pay the price
for your stubbornness.

45:55.670 --> 45:57.160
You leave Sookie out of this.

45:57.880 --> 45:59.996
You're in my house, Mr. Compton.

46:00.174 --> 46:03.462
Put your fangs away.

46:09.809 --> 46:13.552
I'm sorry if it's hard on you being here,
but I gotta work...

46:13.729 --> 46:16.971
...and I am not leaving you alone.

46:17.149 --> 46:21.563
It's hard being anywhere right now.
Might as well be here.

46:22.697 --> 46:24.403
Love you.

46:28.536 --> 46:30.572
[TOILET FLUSHES]

46:31.539 --> 46:33.370
How long you been standing there?

46:36.043 --> 46:38.295
-Because of my shrimp again?
-No.

46:38.462 --> 46:39.872
Good.

46:42.008 --> 46:44.670
Now, I know Coby and Lisa
are part of you...

46:44.844 --> 46:48.086
...and maybe you think I'm not the kind
Of person you want around them.

46:48.264 --> 46:49.800
But--

46:50.474 --> 46:51.725
But I made a list.

46:52.518 --> 46:54.019
A list of what?

46:54.812 --> 46:57.224
Ten reasons why you can trust me
with your kids.

46:58.316 --> 47:00.102
Number one:

47:00.735 --> 47:02.600
I'm a nurturer.

47:02.778 --> 47:06.145
I found a baby armadillo
by the side of the road and I nursed it.

47:06.324 --> 47:09.862
Now it sleeps under my bed,
and its name is Felix.

47:11.454 --> 47:15.697
Number two:
I have a diploma from anger management...

47:15.875 --> 47:19.914
...where I learned talking
about your feelings is the manly thing to do.

47:20.338 --> 47:21.373
Number three--

47:21.547 --> 47:22.912
[GROANS]

47:26.344 --> 47:28.084
[VOMITING AND COUGHING]

47:30.890 --> 47:32.926
Number three:

47:33.100 --> 47:35.933
I never killed nothing by accident.

47:37.438 --> 47:38.553
Number four....

47:52.953 --> 47:54.693
Busy night?

47:56.457 --> 47:57.742
You the only waitress?

47:58.417 --> 48:01.124
Actually, I'm a bartender,
and I ain't working tonight.

48:01.295 --> 48:04.662
-Then what are you doing here?
-Honestly?

48:05.383 --> 48:08.045
Trying not to kill myself.

48:08.594 --> 48:10.425
And how is that going for you?

48:12.515 --> 48:14.380
Well, I'm still alive.

48:14.558 --> 48:16.640
Makes one of us.

48:18.604 --> 48:20.595
You got any of those Tru Bloods?

48:22.233 --> 48:26.272
We only got the B-positive,
and the microwave's busted.

48:27.363 --> 48:30.947
-You a friend of Bill Compton's?
-No.

48:31.617 --> 48:34.484
-Are you?
-Not really.

49:04.483 --> 49:05.518
What the fuck?

49:08.863 --> 49:10.569
Holy shit.

49:16.954 --> 49:18.455
Fuck.

49:19.123 --> 49:21.580
Andy, I'm telling you,
I can walk in a straight line. Look.

49:21.750 --> 49:23.832
ANDY: Mm-hm.
-Like a fucking arrow.

49:24.003 --> 49:26.745
I ain't letting you drive like that.

49:30.134 --> 49:32.716
-Get in.
-Well, this is fun.

49:38.517 --> 49:41.384
I ain't never been in the front seat before.

49:46.025 --> 49:47.686
ROSIE [OVER RADIO]:
Dete ctive Belief/e ur. ..

49:47.860 --> 49:50.226
...we've got a 586 in progress in Hotshot.

49:50.404 --> 49:54.738
Uh, Rosie, you realize a 586
means illegal parking? Over.

49:54.909 --> 49:58.493
ROSIE: Oh. I could have swore
that's what Kenya said.

49:58.662 --> 50:03.577
Anyway, they're busting a meth lab,
whatever the code is for that. Over.

50:05.503 --> 50:07.164
Wanna take a drive?

50:09.256 --> 50:14.000
JASON: Huh. I ain't never been to Hotshot.
ANDY: Nothing to write home about.

50:19.433 --> 50:21.890
Andy, you ain't even on duty.
What are you doing here?

50:22.520 --> 50:25.432
But more importantly,
what is Jason Stackhouse doing here?

50:25.606 --> 50:27.813
-Take two, one--
-Stop it.

50:28.400 --> 50:32.234
-You stay in the car.
-"Stay in the car."

50:33.113 --> 50:35.274
This is my town, Kenya.

50:36.450 --> 50:40.910
And whatever happens in my town
concerns me.

50:41.080 --> 50:44.948
Quit speechifying.
There ain't no cameras here, you damn fool.

50:45.376 --> 50:48.914
You sure did sound smart
on the TV, Andy.

50:49.088 --> 50:50.624
There a problem here, officers?

50:50.798 --> 50:53.585
Calvin Norris, we got a warrant
to search your property.

50:53.759 --> 50:54.794
What for?

50:54.969 --> 50:56.004
[GLASS BREAKING]

50:56.178 --> 50:57.258
Kenya.

50:57.721 --> 51:00.303
CALVIN: Get Off my land, you fucking pigs!
KEVIN: Stand back, sir.

51:00.474 --> 51:03.341
CALVIN: Don't tell me what to do.
You got no fucking right to be here.

51:03.519 --> 51:06.386
KEVIN: Calm down, Mr. Norris.
CALVIN: Calm down? Fuck you.

51:06.564 --> 51:07.895
KEVIN:
I'm an Officer of the law...

51:08.065 --> 51:10.977
...and you are not allowed to say that
to an officer of the law.

51:11.151 --> 51:13.142
That's the law.

51:14.822 --> 51:17.985
ANDY: In there. Inside. I see him.
KENYA: Stop. Andy.

51:18.158 --> 51:19.614
Andy!

51:22.454 --> 51:23.864
Hey.

51:29.128 --> 51:30.288
Are you all right?

51:45.311 --> 51:46.517
AN DY:
Goddamn it, stop!

51:55.446 --> 51:56.526
[BOTH GRUNTING]

51:56.697 --> 51:58.983
AN DY:
Sheriff's Department. Stop!

52:01.827 --> 52:03.533
Hey, I got one.

52:05.164 --> 52:06.654
I got me a drug dealer.

52:16.133 --> 52:18.920
KRIS:
WOO! Big night.

52:20.763 --> 52:22.378
[GLASS BREAKS]

52:25.059 --> 52:26.720
Hey, hey.

52:29.772 --> 52:33.390
SHANE: Ride on that shit. Fuck that shit.
I'll ride that shit like a pony.

52:33.567 --> 52:35.353
Hey, this is where it happened, dude.

52:35.527 --> 52:38.985
Andy put that serial-killer nigger down
right here.

52:42.910 --> 52:45.151
-Oh, shit.
-Hey!

52:45.329 --> 52:47.115
[BOTH CHUCKLE]

52:48.540 --> 52:50.576
Shit. It's the freak's girlfriend.

52:50.751 --> 52:52.992
His name was Eggs,
you racist piece of shit.

52:53.170 --> 52:56.662
Well, you're the one
who went and fucked a killer, bitch.

53:00.052 --> 53:03.260
-Apologize to the lady.
-Serial killer weren't enough for you?

53:03.430 --> 53:05.921
Now you gotta go
fuck a goddamn vampire too?

53:07.851 --> 53:13.687
I said, apologize to the lady.

53:13.857 --> 53:15.188
Fuck you.

53:22.116 --> 53:23.322
[GROWLING]

53:27.705 --> 53:29.696
TALBOT:
Blood gelato.

53:32.000 --> 53:35.242
Sookie has nothing to do with this.
She's innocent.

53:35.421 --> 53:38.629
We know that you love her,
that you've killed for her.

53:39.466 --> 53:42.128
From the look in your eye,
I can see you'd do it again...

53:42.302 --> 53:44.213
...if you thought that would save her.

53:44.805 --> 53:47.012
So romantic.

53:47.182 --> 53:50.640
It's not romantic, it's delusional.

53:51.019 --> 53:52.270
[RUSSELL CHUCKLES]

53:52.438 --> 53:55.601
RUSSELL: Lorena.
-Oh, goodie.

53:56.024 --> 53:57.980
I'm just in time for dessert.

54:03.323 --> 54:04.824
[SCREAMING]

54:12.541 --> 54:15.032
TO have and to hold...

54:15.210 --> 54:17.747
...to love and to cherish...

54:17.921 --> 54:22.210
...to blah, blah, blah, blah, blah,
until death do you part.

54:22.384 --> 54:24.841
Doesn't bother you
that you'll be the only one dying?

54:25.012 --> 54:27.674
-I'm not gonna talk about this with you.
-Okay.

54:30.184 --> 54:33.176
So you'd really rather stay out here
all night than invite me in?

54:33.353 --> 54:36.937
One minute you lie to me,
the next minute you ask me to trust you.

54:37.107 --> 54:40.144
You do something generous
and selfless...

54:40.319 --> 54:45.859
...and then you follow that up
with something nasty or downright cruel.

54:49.203 --> 54:50.238
Invite me in.

54:50.412 --> 54:53.870
-You can't bully your way into--
-Invite me in now.

54:54.041 --> 54:56.828
Mr. Northman, will you please come in?

54:59.171 --> 55:00.661
[GROWLING]

55:03.592 --> 55:05.048
[YELLS]

55:05.761 --> 55:07.171
[GUNSHOT]
